Built for Raspberry pi running headless - Auto Start on boot permissable and recommended
Very simple interface - just a list of web radio stations to play
Scalable - the list can be endless, or accordian style format can display by genre(?)
Has Volume Control AND a Pi Shutdown button from web page
Minimal - only has one python program, one html page, and a csv file 
Customizable - Bootstrap design and components easilly configured
Responsive - hit the play button and enjoy music right away with no buffer
Educational - can be hacked, and if it breaks, go git another one
Modern  - built using bootstrap 4 for latest web technologies
Dorkable - not sure what that means- but seems fitting
Efficient - uses very little power, perfect project for Pi zero w
Personal - no middleman, no advertisements, no tracking nor cookies
